    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An unstable copper trihydroxychloride isomer with a green or blue-green hue. Found in Cornwall, England, Austria, Germany, Greece, and the southwest United States. Sometimes used as a green pigment in painting. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
